gle.com/newspapers?nid=2199&dat=19950506&id=A0YyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=jOYFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4631,1776980&hl=en Genetically Altered Potato Ok'd For Crops] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=2199&dat=19950506&id=A0YyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=jOYFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4631,1776980&hl=en |date=20220417160823 }} Lawrence Journal-World - 6 May 1995</ref>

